assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c781485bfcd7cc8d7a9cc91d407b934f46e621","tid":182583,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"有無性趣番大陸做研究？"},{"pid":"fcf0f5cf8201c0dcd91523a9db38f45ddb7c4323","tid":182583,"uid":597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"想讀+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c483545197c658aa8ffb0075bb9fbebf8bbdee6","tid":182583,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無性趣番大陸做研究？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n研究假野？"},{"pid":"54223ff5a6a08cf85003b048fcb9c9da62058718","tid":182583,"uid":45238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"9c5769894feda75474402ac489d22e43e2bf8abe","tid":182583,"uid":93287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"唉 啲姨媽姑姐就屌冇前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d6c7d51ba2c6bb26ebf38f0ac440a28fda0dca","tid":182583,"uid":60366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:15:05.000Z","msg":"原來之前有個咁既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我講下啦<br />\n我係澳洲讀考古既，上年讀完honours<br />\n係澳洲如果你要做考古學家係<span style=\"color: red;\">一定</span>要有honours以上既學歴<br />\n不過如果你係考古honours fresh graduate+外國人，你係d 澳洲archaeological consultancy搵到 junior archaeologist既工黎做既機會係零<br />\n因為就算一年一間大學出十個honours fresh graduates都好，個市場都唔洗咁多人<br />\n<br />\n而澳洲honours仲有個問題，澳洲honours係難入過master，但係其他國家唔會當你個honours係d乜，所以拎住honours去其他國家搵工亦係好輸蝕<br />\n當時有research master同honours比我揀，我揀左honours，依家好後悔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀商科出身，又真心想讀考古既你我建議你條路咁行<br />\n升讀Grad diploma/ taught master，再讀research master<br />\n而且之後最好有publication，因為好多時考古可以講係一行同academic experience掛勾既行業黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於香港係點既情況呢?　似乎就唔太好<br />\n係香港私人考古公司又唔多，又唔係成日請人<br />\n同埋跟我上面咁講澳洲honours係外國搵工係好蝕章<br />\n所以我依一類recent graduate, 無publication既small potato完全唔期望可以係香港搵到份正式考古學家既工，<br />\n我完左sem半年，一直去下旅行，係外國行下山啊，做下廢青咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家打算過多兩個星期拎埋張testamur番左香港之後send applications自薦做long term volunteer，希望人地肯accept下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而museum啊，research assistant依d工係少, 但係都叫多過香港考古既工<br />\n但係依d工種你就要同其他humanities科爭 (anthropology, history, museum studies etc)<br />\n我幾個月前send過兩份cv亦完全無回覆<br />\n<br />\n順帶一問，你係對乜考古有興趣?<br />\n我係讀prehistoric+settlement archaeology出身既"},{"pid":"5b89d45002c201cfe40d95c79c9bc71eec762bc5","tid":182583,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:21:29.000Z","msg":"讀考古同恐龍扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bb3457395779d1a7f24efc95ba31784e231d3e","tid":182583,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀考古同恐龍扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考古同恐龍無關<br />\n恐龍係交比古生物學家處理"},{"pid":"931380a3de8b9c9214a771467dc49a6a0a0e3091","tid":182583,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:37:43.000Z","msg":"政府"},{"pid":"3ff82e93862e146b2417d14a38b9095b39f65843","tid":182583,"uid":93287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來之前有個咁既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我講下啦<br />\n我係澳洲讀考古既，上年讀完honours<br />\n係澳洲如果你要做考古學家係<span style=\"color: red;\">一定</span>要有honours以上既學歴<br />\n不過如果你係考古honours fresh graduate+外國人，你係d 澳洲archaeological consultancy搵到 junior archaeologist既工黎做既機會係零<br />\n因為就算一年一間大學出十個honours fresh graduates都好，個市場都唔洗咁多人<br />\n<br />\n而澳洲honours仲有個問題，澳洲honours係難入過master，但係其他國家唔會當你個honours係d乜，所以拎住honours去其他國家搵工亦係好輸蝕<br />\n當時有research master同honours比我揀，我揀左honours，依家好後悔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀商科出身，又真心想讀考古既你我建議你條路咁行<br />\n升讀Grad diploma/ taught master，再讀research master<br />\n而且之後最好有publication，因為好多時考古可以講係一行同academic experience掛勾既行業黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於香港係點既情況呢?　似乎就唔太好<br />\n係香港私人考古公司又唔多，又唔係成日請人<br />\n同埋跟我上面咁講澳洲honours係外國搵工係好蝕章<br />\n所以我依一類recent graduate, 無publication既small potato完全唔期望可以係香港搵到份正式考古學家既工，<br />\n我完左sem半年，一直去下旅行，係外國行下山啊，做下廢青咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家打算過多兩個星期拎埋張testamur番左香港之後send applications自薦做long term volunteer，希望人地肯accept下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而museum啊，research assistant依d工係少, 但係都叫多過香港考古既工<br />\n但係依d工種你就要同其他humanities科爭 (anthropology, history, museum studies etc)<br />\n我幾個月前send過兩份cv亦完全無回覆<br />\n<br />\n順帶一問，你係對乜考古有興趣?<br />\n我係讀prehistoric+settlement archaeology出身既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我對古代歷史有興趣，例如古希臘古埃及，但係由於以前係讀商科，加上對考古學嘅前途認識不大，我朋友都係叫我讀Bachelor of Archaeology先，聽巴打咁講真係要讀上去先有啲前途，  而且我係想畢完業返香港搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw唔該巴打提供咁多資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}